    "[96] leveraged the inherent relationship between CG and CS and utilized pre-trained models to enhance the accuracy of the code generation task.",
    "Code generation on top of existing codeSeveral studies have observed that generating code based on existing related code fragments can yield superior performance compared to generating code from scratch.",
    "As a result, these studies incorporate code search techniques and leverage DL to construct their code generators.",
    "For instance, Hashimoto et al. [97] and Kulal et al.",
    "[98] employed DL-based retrieval models to generate Python and C++ code."
